attributes.title: bad
attributes.review: itachi uchiha was a jonin of the hidden leaf village, belonging to the uchiha clan. Due to a long history of discrimination, the Uchiha devised a coup d’ta to overthrow the current hidden leaf government. Split between his loyalty to village and clan, Itachi reported to the Third Hokage and Lord Danzo. Despite the Third Hokage being against the idea of killing the clan, Lord Danzo gave Itachi orders to kill. Itachi killed everyone in his clan. His parents, his lover, but not his younger brother, Sasuke Uchiha. Itachi defected from the hidden leaf and joined the Akatsuki, while secretly reporting to the Third Hokage. Year later, Sasuke has become a genin hellbent on killing Itachi for revenge against his clan’s killer.
